item.comments: I agree with Debra French. The Meetup group "Meet Singles 40 Plus" charges $15 with NO food or drink obligation or assignment. Join it for free (on Meetup.com) & see all their events. Enjoy the party & please honor our Armed Forces on Memorial Day.
